Package: reportabs
Title: Makes Reporting ABS Time Series Data Simpler
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Hamish",
           family = "Gamble",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "hamish.gamble@flinders.edu.au")
Description: Makes reporting ABS TimeSeries data simpler. 
  It provides convenience functions for plotting labour market indicators, and for reporting of changes in
  indicators over time. Links with the aitidata package. 
